Group:      System/Libraries
Requires:   libsailfishcrypto = %{version}-%{release}

%description -n libsailfishcrypto-devel
%{summary}.

%package -n libsailfishcrypto-doc
Summary: Documentation for Sailfish OS Crypto Library
